              "free_text": [
                "",
                "total element yield both for post-neutron emission",
                "derived from fits to isotopic independent yield",
                "distributions"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Ternary fission independent yields were calculated from",
                "the corresponding known binary fission yields (taken",
                "from 'monit-ref') and the measured ternary/binary",
                "ratios of gamma-rays (subentry 2).",
                "The isotopic ternary yield distributions (i.e. with",
                "z=const) obtained were fitted using gaussians. The",
                "parameters derived from the fit are (for each element)",
                " - the width of the distribution"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "1",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " - the position of the maximum, which is the most",
                "   probable mass"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "2",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " - the integral over the distribution, which is the",
                "   total yield of a given fission product element"
              ]
            }
          ],
